    <!-- my section -->
    <section class="my-services" id="services">
      <h2 class="section__title section__title--services">What I do</h2>
      <div class="services">
        <div class="service">
          <h3>Web Design</h3>
          <p>
            Designing is the essential step to build a fully functional website. 
            When desinging a product, I focus on UX/UI principles to make sure the experience of a client is optimal.
            I use tools like Adobe photoshop to make logos and fix images, and Figma to create wireframes and prototypes.

          </p>
          </div>

          <div class="service">
          <h3>Web Development</h3>
          <p>
            In development phase. I code the user interface with HTML and CSS. I focus on the adaptive and responsive design.
            I use Express js to build single page or multiple page web apps based on Node js.
            In collaboration, I follow Agile methodoloty, and use tools like Git, GitHub, Google Docs, Miro.com, and Discord
            to communicate effectively with partners.
          </p></div>

          <div class="service">
          <h3>Database</h3>
          <p>
            Database is another essential part for a functional web app, it stores all the information of the users, 
            customers, and inventories ect. A good designed database is organized and easy to maintain. 
            I use MySQL Database to connect to the website data, and I love designing a database and writing SQL queries.
          </p>
        </div>

    </div>
    <a href="#work" class="btn">My Work</a>
    </section>
    <!-- about me -->
