        <p>
          I am currently a Full-Stack Web Development student at BCIT (British
          Columbia Institute of Technology). This is a 2 years program, and I am currently in the second year.
          <!-- When it comes to make something practical and beatiful, I always present my full passion into building the products that would make usersâ€™ life better.  -->
        </p>

        <p>
          My first exposure to coding was when I took the OAT
          (Office Administrator with Techknowledgy) program at BCIT. In this
          program, I became a certified specialist with Microsoft Office suite.
          More importantly, I learned some basic Front-end programming in HTML
          and CSS. This helped me to discover my inner passion for programming.
        </p>
        <!-- link to idsp project -->
        <p>
          After two years of working in the office environment, I finally made the
          decistion to start my coding career in September of 2021. After one
          year of intense learning and training, I not only learned
